caller_intent: The caller wanted to confirm and process a payment for their rent insurance, ensuring the correct payment method was used.
resolution_steps: Agent accessed the caller's account to retrieve payment details.
Confirmed the payment amount ($19.68) and asked the caller to specify their preferred payment method.
Agent processed the payment and confirmed it was already processed.
Agent verified no further action was needed and closed the call.
knowledge_required: Accessing customer accounts to retrieve payment information
systems_referenced: Payment system (implied through 'pull up' and 'processed' references)
summary: The caller confirmed a rent insurance payment of $19.68 using their MasterCard. The agent processed the payment and verified its success. The caller had no further requests, and the call concluded with confirmation of payment completion.
